*Saznam* da je ona odlazila u ponedeljak (I found out that she was leaving on Monday). 

Ona je *saznala* da je njen brat zaradio dobre ocene (She found out that her brother earned good grades).

Moj kolega je *saznao* za moju novu poslovnu priliku (My colleague found out about my new business opportunity).

Ja sam *saznao* da će biti oblačno tokom vikenda (I found out that it will be cloudy during the weekend). 

Oni su *saznali* da je njihova kuća u opasnosti (They found out that their house was in danger).